Changes: * Fixed an issue when production server could not print qr codes.

Changes: * Added modular window for a website's qr printing for mass_qr prints with modular window.
Changes: * Added modular window for a website's qr printing in 4th version print. * Code cleanup. Removed some comented out code, which is no longer being used.
Changes: * Fixed an one qr per multiple serial printing on two rows issue.
Changes: * Added back missed ">" in v5 computer_edit
Changes: * Added functionality to search, add and remove observations in computer_edit_v5.
Changes: * Added changelog.

Changes: * "Box No." in Excel and CSV moved as the last column.

Changes:
* Finished front end is working for ramsticks, processors and gpus templates. * Minor changes to ensure that data set on website would be sent to the server and clear distinction between new entities and existing ones. * Minor change to observation to template "computer_search_from_order_row" to contain box_number. * Rewritten code in views(website) and logic(website) to remove duplicating code in regards to searches. * And removed some old commented out irrelevant code from logic(website).

Changes: * Wrapped up version5 computer manual adding to a system. * Removed obsolete code. * Entities are created/retrieved and connections are properly created to save v5 computers. * Minor changes everywhere to improve compatibilities.

Changes: * Added new table ComputerFormFactors and reference to it from Computers. * Added link on leftMenuSubTemplate as a placeholder for future ComputerFormFactors table managment. * Updated changelog.md with changes in new_record brief explanation.

Changes: * Added new table ComputerFormFactors and reference to it from Computers. * Added link on leftMenuSubTemplate as a placeholder for future ComputerFormFactors table managment. * Updated changelog.md with changes in new_record brief explanation.
* Implemented ComputerFormFactors functionality fully. * Updated changelog.md to reflect changes. * Places where ComputerFormFactors should be interacted with has been implemented: * Client program interaction: get aux_data2, get/post data2. * New record adding allows setting form factor. (empty string sets id to null/None) * Editing record allows edditing record. (empty string sets id to null/None) * Computer viewing table allows filtering by form factor. * Rewritten some code both in ULDCTinterface and website logic files to simplify the code. * More stuff, but all the rest are mere details.

Changes: * Rewritten some function based views and functions in logic(website) to simplify code, make fewer function calls and shorten code length. Nothing serious though.
TODO: * Complete simplification of Observer code.
Changes: * Removed get_all_observations_dict. No use of this function were found.
Changes: * Cleaned up some more code.
Changes: * Cleaned up some even more code. * Removed obsolete code. * Refractoring some other code. * Changing previous urls from "aux_data2", "data2" to "aux_data", "data"
Changes: * Decided to leave "aux_data2", "data2" with "aux_data", "data" for now, just in case.
Changes: * Fixed issue where updating computer record from client program doesn't update form_factor.

Changes: * Added new alt_data(combination of data and aux_data) to interact with client program as per request. * logic(website) ComputerToEdit.process_post() altered pops, so it wouldn't crash when any of them are missing on the website.

Changes: * Changed the way CSV/Excel files are exported. * If at least one computer is desktop all computers are exported in a desktop structure. * Otherwise all computers are exported in laptop structure.
Changes: * Updated changelog.md to reflect changes to csv/excel generation.

Changes: * Added showing of category in computer search from order. * Fixed an issue where computer search from order was returning sold computers and computers belonging to other orders. * Updated changelog regarding these changes.

Changes: * Added three types of buttons in hdd_edit to open computers, lots and orders. * Split some javascript code to hdd_edit.js to avoid confusion. * Rewritten some javascript changing in some places hdd to drive. * Removed duplicate code to simplify reading.
Changes: * Updated changelog.md regarding changes with new buttons in hdd_edit.

Changes: * Fixed an issue distorted design in observation details page. * Changed html structure to limit distortions. * Changed css to accomodate changes in html. * Rewritten revealSubcategories to showSubcategories and revealShortcodes to showDetails in order to make them more compatible with different html and css. Also some changes to make code less repetitive.
Changes: * Added drive removal functionality in computer_edit_v5. * Rewritten some code in computer_edit_v5.js to remove some of the code repetitiveness. * Updated changelog.md about the changes.

Changes: * Extended website computer filtering of cpus/gpus to many_to_many relationships. * Changed website computer filtering using other, by removing comment filtering, instead it filters according to observations. * Updated changelog to reflect these changes.
Changes: * Implemented quantity showing in parenthesis next to computer filtering choices. * Updated changolog.md about these changes.

Changes: * Implemented quantity showing in parenthesis next to drives filtering choices. * buttons in all storages now positioned horizontally. * Main table in main page no longer drops down. * Updated changolog.md about these changes.
Changes: * Fixed issue regarding lot_content and hdd_order table distortions when changing window sizes.
Changes: * Extended search functionality with 5v fields. * Updated changelog.md with changes.
Changes: * Implemented global search result filtering by status functionality. * Updated changelog.md with changes.

Changes: * Rewritten some code of HddToEdit in order to simplify the code and make it use less memory. * Removed unnecessary print statements.
Changes: * Partially done 4v removal progress. * Backing up in new branch because this process should later on be resumed.
Changes: * Added ramstick removal from computer in the computer_edit functionality.

Changes: * Updated changelog to about the changes. * Simplified remove_drive_from_computer, remove_observation_from_computer and remove_ramstick_from_computer by moving repeating code to remove_object_from_computer.
Changes: * Added functionality to add empty ramstick. * Found and fixed bug related to saving changed ram type of ramstick. * Updated changelog.
Changes: * Fixed bug where ramstick removal is not present when adding nonexistant ramstick.
Changes: * Removing ramstick updates total_ram based on sum of remaining rams.
Changes: * Automatic ramstick adding functionality. * Updated changelog.
Changes: * Simplified some code, removed unnecessary classes and functions.
Changes: * Trash cleaning of 4th version code and unecessary files.
Changes: * ULCDTinterface cleanup from 4v remains.
